# Documentation language

- All reports and documentation under **`/docs`** must be written in **English**.
- Use the naming convention `xxxx-report-yyyyy.md` (e.g. `0001-report-models.md`).
- When creating or editing any file in `docs/`, write titles, headings, body text, tables, and code comments in English.
